{
  "stem": "24346.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, we are talking, now, before the ghetto was created.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mind you, I'm going back, because this incident-- I just, where you asked me, so I'm going back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was before the ghetto was closed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I want to make it clear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Lodz, I told you before, was an industrial city-- textile.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we could get things in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't official, it was more like a black market.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But things that weren't available there in Krasnik Lubelski, where we went.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So an older cousin of mine, who was also a relative from this area, said, let's go to Lodz, bring some stuff and sell it here.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We could buy it, let's say, for one-fifth the price-- but the going price that was there, you could buy it, because we had the let's say, the resources, so much.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had the people-- we knew the people to go to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went, we took yarn that you need to sew in rolls.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't on little spools, but it was big rolls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We put it on our body, a few.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we traveled back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was very rewarding, because we made money, and we could buy food on the black market.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was very good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one time, my mother and I-- when my mother said, I do it with my cousin-- said, how about if I go, too?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could double.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a good thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We know where to buy it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People from there don't know where to get the outlets, where to get it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we did that for awhile.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "However, we didn't know when they were going to close the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So one time we went, and my mother and I were stuck in the ghetto and couldn't get back out.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
